          <p class="text-gray-700">Week 1: 237 trials (from 5,000 visitors) = 4.7% conversion. Week 2: Added integration showcase (QuickBooks, Xero, Google Sheets) = 312 trials. Week 3: Added live chat for questions = 387 trials. Week 4: A/B tested "See How It Works" video placement = 4.7% ‚Üí 6.1% conversion. Month 1: 1,847 trials, 187 paid conversions. Month 2: 2,231 trials, 312 paid conversions. Month 3: 2,891 trials, 447 paid conversions = $89K MRR.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-[3px] border-indigo-500 pl-6 py-5 bg-white rounded-r mb-6">
          <p class="text-sm font-black text-indigo-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE 90-DAY BREAKDOWN</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Month 1:</strong> 0.8% ‚Üí 4.7% conversion rate. 5,000 visitors ‚Üí 237 trials vs 40 before. Specific value prop = instant understanding. Demo video = see it work = trust = sign up. Transparent pricing = can afford = start trial. One-click signup = frictionless = convert now.<br><strong>Month 2:</strong> Added integration showcase, live chat. 5,000 visitors ‚Üí 312 trials. Integrations visible = works with my tools = sign up. Live chat = get answers = convert now.<br><strong>Month 3:</strong> 6.1% conversion rate stabilized. 2,891 trials, 447 paid = $89K MRR. David: "I spent $1,200 on the landing page. Was spending $8K/month on ads getting 40 trials. Now getting 2,891 trials. Same ad spend, 72x more signups. ROI: Impossible to calculate. Clear value props = trials convert = business grows."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE HARD TRUTH -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-indigo-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-4xl">
