          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">"Used by 500+ companies" with logos = others trust it = safe = sign up. No proof = risky = skip. Social proof visible = 53% more signups.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 border-l-[3px] border-red-500 rounded-r">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">‚ùå Signup Friction (5+ fields)</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">7 fields = friction = they leave. One-click trial with email only = convert now. Every extra field = 20-30% drop-off. Frictionless = 43% more signups.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 border-l-[3px] border-red-500 rounded-r">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">‚ùå No Integrations Visible</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">"Works with Slack, Notion, Google Sheets" visible = fits my stack = sign up. Hidden integrations = will it work? = skip. Integrations = reduce risk = sign up.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- UNEXPECTED FINDINGS -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-[#EEF2FF]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-5xl">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-blue-50 border-[3px] border-indigo-400 p-8 md:p-10">
