          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-indigo-700 mb-2">üéØ SaaS-Specific Templates</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Pre-built templates designed for SaaS: hero with value prop + CTA, feature showcase, pricing table, integration logos, testimonial carousel, FAQ, one-click trial. Everything converts. Just customize content.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-indigo-700 mb-2">üéØ Lightning-Fast Load Times</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Framer sites load in 1.2 seconds. Every 0.1s faster = 1% more conversions. Fast site = they see content = sign up. Slow sites = they bounce = you lose them.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-indigo-700 mb-2">üéØ CMS for Features & Integrations</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Dynamic feature pages, integration showcase. Add new feature, it appears across site. Update pricing, changes everywhere. CMS = maintainable = always current = always converting.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WEBFLOW & SQUARESPACE BREAKDOWNS -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="border-[3px] border-gray-300 p-6 rounded-lg">
